I've said it in the past on other uploads.
Once the shells stripped and ready, get in touch with Craig at Buzzweld for the anti corrosion and wheel arch/underbody treatment plus inside the engine bay, boot and interior befor carpet etc goes in.
His products are the best on the market and will protect Binky from almost anything.
He can supply you or get the shell to him.
I'm sure if asked he can get all the treatments made up in the final body colours as well!
I still say it would look the nuts if a set of massive Minilites were on it!
A long time coming but I cant wait.

snippet.textDisplay: Have you tested those tow anchors with side loads?  They look like they were designed to close fit into a socket up to the big shoulder.
